data.title: List of parishes under the jurisdiction of the bishop of Lincoln
data.text:
Diocese page | Bishops list | Sources list | Location list | Source essay | Jurisdiction list

This page provides links to all parishes under the jurisdiction of the bishop of Lincoln. Thus, it includes peculiars outside the diocese that are under his jurisdiction, but excludes all peculiars within the diocese. Clicking on the name of the parish will take you to the Database entry for that parish.
